Usage: ARINWIN on|user|both|off
  Toggles showing auto reply in current/special window

  If set to on auto-reply is also shown in current window.
  If set to user auto-reply is shown in window with level USERLOG4.
  If set to both auto-reply is shown both in current window and
  in window with level USERLOG4.

See also:
  REPWORD
